` 在故障期间最大值达到 16,198,575.26，而正常期间为 289,263.56。\n   - `rrt`: `cartservice` 的中值从 1,348.41 增加到 274,717.54。\n   - `rrt_max`: 在 `checkoutservice` 中变化显著，从 201,612.0 增加到 14,860,153.0。\n\n由于没有 Node 级别的严重问题，且问题主要集中在服务层面，因此假设这些服务的请求延迟和吞吐量受限是合理的。\n\n### 结论\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"rrt\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significantly increased rrt and rrt_max indicating performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice rrt increased from 1348.41 to 274717.54, rrt_max increased from 3223.0 to 2554345.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significantly increased rrt_max indicating performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice rrt_max increased from 201612.0 to 14860153.0.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significantly increased rrt_max indicating performance degradation.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend rrt_max increased from 226820.0 to 14781736.0.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n这些服务的严重延迟表现清楚地表明性能瓶颈，与检测到的系统异常相吻合。在没有 Node 资源耗尽或 Pod 崩溃的情况下，假设问题是由于服务间的瓶颈引起的是合乎逻辑的。", "current_hypothesis": "Cartservice 是系统异常的根因，由于其显著的延迟和性能退化，导致下游服务（如 CheckoutService）依赖请求的全部链路受限。"}
